</HEADLINE>
 
 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    THE MACONDO TIMES. Colombia's Gabriel Garcia Marquez is making
headlines _ his own.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-GABRIEL-GARCIA-MARQUEZ-LATINTRADE-NYTSF.
