40 points, or 0.4 percent, and the Nasdaq index was off 25 points,
or 1 percent. Elsewhere, prices rose 0.7 percent in Tokyo and
jumped 4.4 percent in Hong Kong. They fell 0.9 percent in Frankfurt
and 0.7 percent in London. They increased 2.2 percent in Brazil and
1.6 percent in Mexico. On the American debt market, the long bond
was off 8/32 point.
