   LOUISIANA-KOSOVO-REACT. Southeast Louisiana lawmakers remain
split along partisan lines about what to do in Kosovo. (600 words.)
By Mark Stricherz
</P>
<P>
   MASSACHUSETTS-RESERVE-SUPPORT. Massachusetts lawmakers said
Friday they will support President Clinton if he decides to call up
33,000 U.S. reservists to help augment NATO troops serving in
Yugoslavia. (500 words.) By Mark D. Preston
</P>
