   The New York Times plans these stories in conjunction with the
retirement of hockey great Wayne Gretzky.
</P>
<P>
   Eds, this story is intended for newspage or sportspage use:
</P>
<P>
   HKN-GRETZKY (New York) _ Wayne Gretzky, among the greatest
hockey players ever, announces his retirement. By Joe Lapointe.
</P>
