   THOMPSON-COLUMN (Washington) _ When the bombing ends and peace
is restored, Kosovo will need a Marshall Plan like the one that
rebuilt Western Europe after World War II. A look at how that plan
came about 52 years ago. By ROBERT E. THOMPSON. (Filed Wednesday.)
